query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(a1 q1 s t1 tq1 u1) */ select t1.name,
count(*)
from tag_question AS tq1
inner join question AS q1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.favorite_count >= 5 AND q1.favorite_count <= 5000
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('analysis',
'combinatorics',
'complex-analysis',
'functional-analysis',
'general-topology',
'inequality',
'matrices',
'probability')
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('askubuntu',
'math')
inner join answer AS a1
on s.site_id = a1.site_id AND a1.question_id = q1.id
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.reputation >= 0 AND u1.reputation <= 100 group by t1.name;
